Text:
Fake! All the songs are out of order. For example: The official Top 5 of the 1963 Top 100 are:

   1  Surfin USA - Beach Boys
   2  The End Of The World - Skeeter Davis
   3  Rhythm Of The Rain - Cascades
   4  He's So Fine - Chiffons
   5  Blue Velvet  - Bobby Vinton

I have the Billboard book by Joe edwards that has all the top 100s listed.
